WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
Downloaded From www.AllSubs.org

00:00.900 --> 00:03.900
 Remember, do not try anything
 you are about to see at home.

00:07.941 --> 00:10.941
 Ohh!

00:12.045 --> 00:15.045
 NARRATOR: On this salivating
 episode of "Mythbusters"...

00:15.615 --> 00:17.516
 Burn!

00:17.517 --> 00:19.718
 NARRATOR:
...Adam and Jamie regurgitate

00:19.719 --> 00:21.453
 a "Seinfeld" classic.

00:21.454 --> 00:22.421
 I'm sorry.

00:22.422 --> 00:25.357
 NARRATOR: Is double dipping
 really germ warfare?

00:25.358 --> 00:26.592
 [ Gagging ]

00:26.593 --> 00:29.593
 Plus, they're falling
 over themselves...

00:29.996 --> 00:30.829
 [ Ding ]

00:30.830 --> 00:32.965
...finding out if a banana peel

00:32.966 --> 00:35.966
 is a guaranteed
 slapstick wipeout.

00:36.236 --> 00:37.736
 I've never seen him like that.

00:37.737 --> 00:40.339
 NARRATOR:
 Meanwhile, Kari, Grant, and Tory

00:40.340 --> 00:42.808
 have a blast...

00:42.809 --> 00:44.610
 That was awesome!

00:44.611 --> 00:47.012
 NARRATOR:... and cook up trouble
 as they tackle the myth

00:47.013 --> 00:49.314
 of homemade diamonds.

00:49.315 --> 00:50.649
 I'm gonna be rich!

00:50.650 --> 00:52.651
 NARRATOR:
 So prepare yourselves.

00:52.652 --> 00:54.620
 -There's thrills...
 -Aghh!

00:54.621 --> 00:56.288
 NARRATOR:... spills...

00:56.289 --> 00:59.289
 and the biggest explosion
 in "Mythbusters" history.

01:05.432 --> 01:07.933
 Who are the Mythbusters?

01:07.934 --> 01:09.768
 Adam Savage...

01:09.769 --> 01:11.770
 Oh, check out
 my new bulletproof vest, man!

01:11.771 --> 01:13.172
 NARRATOR:
...and Jamie Hyneman.

01:13.173 --> 01:15.074
 I usually don't let
 people do that.

01:15.075 --> 01:17.209
 NARRATOR:
 Between them, more than 30 years

01:17.210 --> 01:19.211
 of special-effects experience.

01:19.212 --> 01:20.979
 I'm not gonna get tired of that.

01:20.980 --> 01:23.582
 NARRATOR:
 Joining them...

01:23.583 --> 01:24.917
...Grant Imahara...

01:24.918 --> 01:27.918
 -You beauty!
 -NARRATOR:... Tory Belleci...

01:28.188 --> 01:30.656
 -[ Glass shatters, alarm wails ]
 -Ugh!

01:30.657 --> 01:31.857
 NARRATOR:
...and Kari Byron.

01:31.858 --> 01:33.625
 Bustin' out of here, see?

01:33.626 --> 01:35.494
 NARRATOR:
 They don't just tell the myths.

01:35.495 --> 01:38.495
 They put them to the test.

